casebody.data:
No. 204,

Misc.

Frankfeld et al. v. United States. Joseph Forer, Royal W. France and Harold Buchman for petitioners. Acting Solicitor General Stern, Assistant Attorney General Murray, Beatrice Rosenberg, Murry Lee Randall and Edward S. Szukel-ewicz for the United States.

C. A. 4th Cir. Motions for leave to file briefs of National Lawyers Guild and John Abt et al., as amici curiae, denied. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Black and Mr. Justice Douglas are of the opinion certiorari should be granted.
